  "detailed_description": "Energy Invasion - an arcade game inspired by the classic Breakout. Unlike the original game, your ball does not break blocks on its own, but can launch missiles in a chosen direction. The game is designed for a controller, but the ability to control with the keyboard and mouse is also present.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- A lot of bonuses (both useful and harmful)<br />\r\n- Bright graphic effects<br />\r\n- Levels with dangerous enemies<br />\r\n- Soundtrack from Nick R 61 (19 tracks in the game and 7 bonus-tracks, available separately)<br />\r\n- 25 levels in \"Invasion\" mode, 25 levels in \"Linear\" mode, ∞ levels in \"Endless\" mode",
  "about_the_game": "Energy Invasion - an arcade game inspired by the classic Breakout. Unlike the original game, your ball does not break blocks on its own, but can launch missiles in a chosen direction. The game is designed for a controller, but the ability to control with the keyboard and mouse is also present.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- A lot of bonuses (both useful and harmful)<br />\r\n- Bright graphic effects<br />\r\n- Levels with dangerous enemies<br />\r\n- Soundtrack from Nick R 61 (19 tracks in the game and 7 bonus-tracks, available separately)<br />\r\n- 25 levels in \"Invasion\" mode, 25 levels in \"Linear\" mode, ∞ levels in \"Endless\" mode",
